            <item>
                <title>千秋岁引</title>
                <link>https://zhimaye.cc/posts/%E5%8D%83%E7%A7%8B%E5%B2%81%E5%BC%95/</link>
                <guid isPermaLink="true">https://zhimaye.cc/posts/%E5%8D%83%E7%A7%8B%E5%B2%81%E5%BC%95/</guid>
                <pubDate>Sun, 19 Sep 2021 14:17:58 &#43;0800</pubDate>
                
                    <author>flumine@163.com (二十三点)</author>
                
                <copyright>[CC BY-NC-SA 4.0](https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/deed.zh)</copyright>
                
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;初见春山，秋波流睇，浅笑低眉便合意。枝头戏燕相私语，心中已定今生事。只未料，情根种，深至此。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;辗转春秋来复去。笑泪俱成云烟耳。相思种种如初识。连天弱水三千里，何如眼前一知己。愿白发，仍相依，如今日。&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
                
                
                
                
                
                    
                        
                            
                                
                                
                                
